---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead
			title="About Me | TikaTiles"
			description="Background for the founder of TikaTiles."
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>About Me</h1>
			<p>
				<strong>Technical Leader in Embedded Systems & Machine Learning</strong>
			</p>
			<p>
				With over 15 years of experience, I specialize in establishing systems architecture and
				leading high-impact ML integration for resource-constrained consumer electronics. My career
				is defined by driving end-to-end product lifecycles - from scaling custom RTOS firmware for
				Apple's AirPods and Airpods Max lineup to delivering gesture inference improvements for
				millions of users on Ray-Ban Meta smart glasses.
			</p>
			<p>
				Currently based in Orange County, my work exists at the intersection of hardware development
				and engineering automation. Over the last two years, I have deeply integrated agentic AI into
				my daily operations, authoring detailed engineering plans to direct multiple simultaneous
				agents in autonomous code generation.
			</p>
			<p>
				In my personal lab, I am exploring new device architectures and am currently prototyping
				screen-free, tactile toys that rely on physical mechanics and audio rather than digital
				displays - the perfect project as I intentionally step away from the screens this summer to
				soak up quality time with my daughter.
			</p>
			<p>Connect with me:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ritikagoel23/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a></li>
				<li><a href="https://github.com/ritikagoel-lab" target="_blank">GitHub</a></li>
			</ul>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
